              "library": "H5P.Text 1.1",
              "text": "<p><strong>Malasutla</strong><br />\nKahulugan: Makinis at malambot na parang seda.<br />\nHalimbawa: Malasutla ang buhok ni Maria Blanca matapos suklayin.<br />\n<br />\n </p>\n"
